## 📖 Overview

The **BlockDAG DeFi Platform** brings the power of decentralized finance to users with:
- ⚡ Ultra-fast and parallel transaction handling (via DAG-based backend)
- 💸 Decentralized borrowing and lending
- 🔄 Secure and transparent token swaps
- 🎁 NFT rewards based on DeFi achievements
- 👛 Wallet-first experience with live portfolio tracking

---

## ✨ Features

### 🔄 Token Swap
- Real-time price fetching
- Slippage protection
- Live fee & price impact display
- Example: `1 ETH = 2300 USDC`

### 💸 Borrow & Lend
- Borrow crypto using overcollateralization
- Lend assets and earn interest (APY)
- Track health factor and avoid liquidation
- Real-time liquidity stats

### 🎁 NFT Reward System
- Earn NFTs based on platform achievements (e.g., farming, liquidity provision)
- View & claim NFTs tied to wallet

### 📊 Dashboard & Analytics
- TVL, APY, active users, earnings
- Visual graphs of portfolio performance
- Wallet balance, transaction history

