## 🧱 Tech Stack

### 🎨 Frontend
- React + TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Recharts / Chart.js for analytics
- Wagmi + RainbowKit for wallet connection
- Ethers.js / Viem for smart contract interaction

### ⛓️ Smart Contracts
- Solidity (Hardhat framework)
- OpenZeppelin (ERC-20, ERC-721 templates)
- Deployed on EVM-compatible BlockDAG network (Fantom / Kaspa-like)

### 🌐 Backend (optional)
- Node.js + Express
- MongoDB (user metadata, history)
- The Graph / Moralis for indexing

### 🧪 Dev Tools
- Hardhat (smart contract testing/deployment)
- Postman (API testing)
- Docker + GitHub Actions (CI/CD)

